title: John Deere 's total assets 2013 to 2019
yAxis: Total assets in million U.S. dollars
summary: In general Total assets in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Total assets in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2013 to 2016, and lastly slightly increasing from 2016 to 2017.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Total assets in million U.S. dollars, of value 65786.3 was reached at Year 2017
Minimum Total assets in million U.S. dollars about 57947.6 was reached at Year 2015
